config QCOM_MINIDUMP_CLK
	bool "QCOM Minidump clocks Support"
	depends on QCOM_MINIDUMP
	help
	  Enables clock information collection in minidump, with clocks registered
	  to minidump being collected as minidump entries during a crash.
	  Say Y if you want to register the clocks with minidump framework and
	  collect their info in minidump.

